Description: RDF version of the official case law dataset of the Netherlands Council of the Judiciary (at [http://www.rechtspraak.nl](http://www.rechtspraak.nl)). It contains approximately 145k descriptions of court proceedings- linked to DBPedia and Geonames (places mentioned in cases). It contains all Dutch courts and their locations.URIs are dereferenceable.Example: [http://linkeddata.few.vu.nl/rechtspraak/uitspraak/BM4461](http://linkeddata.few.vu.nl/rechtspraak/uitspraak/BM4461)This dataset was developed within the BEST project at the VU University Amsterdam.
